name: Self Polarity #1
description:
A part of me is filled with love, another part with anger.
A part of me meditates, another part submerges in anxiety or nostalgia.
A part of me wants to be someone, another part wants to disappear.
A part of me is me, the other part as well.

We are incongruent, we are opposite extremes.

The series Self Polarity by Vitor Schietti gains its own animated GIFs as collectible NFTs.
